text: Please join me and these beauties for #SwansForRelief. 32 ballerinas from 14 countries have come together to raise funds for dancers around the world impacted by the COVID-19 pandemic. Please go to YouTube to see the **FULL VIDEO** and fundraiser details. Search swans for Relief. https://t.co/v6xcJCuPoh
